{"tid":903790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"囝囝滿月 Coffee林芊妤貼哺乳相引網民罵戰","createTime":"2018-11-16T00:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T13:11:54.000Z","uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f78094af6b368cd110d185c6cdec64ac64b928dc","tid":903790,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T00:02:53.000Z","msg":"滿月喇！林芊妤（Coffee）上月16日一索得男，生咗7磅重「咖啡仔」，日前Coffee透露囝囝已經改咗中文名翟德彥。今日係彥彥滿月大日子，坐完月嘅Coffee為隆重其事，就喺Ig貼咗一張溫馨滿滿嘅餵母乳相。<br />\n呢張充滿愛嘅溫馨照，上載咗短短兩個鐘，已經吸引3萬幾個網民讚好，好多網民都留言，大讚Coffee偉大，唔少媽咪仲話希望多啲人支持餵哺母乳，其他留言就包括「哺乳媽媽最美」、「滿滿的母愛」、「好羨慕啊 個胸型重咁靚」.......<br />\n當然，呢啲嘢永遠都有正反方，亦有網民接受唔到Coffee將餵母乳嘅相公開，留言質疑佢點解要咁做，好似話「餵咪餵點解要咁影俾人睇，都做咗人阿媽都仲係咁」，又話要unfollow佢。不過，大部份網民都好支持Coffee，仲因為力挺Coffee而與反對嘅網民爆罵戰，Coffee亦有回應網民：「其實只係一張好正常嘅相，相信我以前嘅泳衣相都性感過呢張啩？哈哈，我覺得今日係我第一個BB滿月嘅日子，想好好地喺自己平台post呢張相嚟紀念今日，因為其實係好幸福嘅事。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gXD0w3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgXD0w3D.jpg&h=5ad61c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCbxoai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCbxoai.jpg&h=497910c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNpu9Qj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNpu9Qj.jpg&h=18dc786d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ossWvj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ossWvj.jpg&h=63098cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMsHLoF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMsHLoF.jpg&h=91fea97b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2BQUg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2BQUg0.jpg&h=f7c75476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbhP9Qm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbhP9Qm.jpg&h=6eabe9f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ef9d06c00d4